\c 99 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 99\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Guddina Waaqayyoo Ol Ol Kaasuu 
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo mootii dha, sababii kanaaf sabni hundinuu in rom'a! Inni teessoo isaa isa Kiruubel baatan irra jira, sababii kanaaf lafti in socho'a.
\m \bd 2\bd* Waaqayyo Xiyoonitti guddaa dha, inni saba hundumaa irratti ol jedhaa dha.
\m \bd 3\bd* Maqaa kee isa guddaadhaa fi isa sodaatamaadhaafis galata haa galchan! Inni dhuguma qulqulluu dha.
\m \bd 4\bd* Aangoon mootichaa, wanta dhugaa ta'e in jaallata; ati wanta qajeelaa ta'e jabeessitee dhaabdeetta, dhugaan, qajeelummaanis Yaaqoob keessatti akka argamu gooteetta.
\m \bd 5\bd* Waaqayyoon gooftaa keenya ulfinaan ol kaasaa, ejjeta miilla isaa jalatti isaaf sagadaa! Inni dhuguma qulqulluu dha.
\m \bd 6\bd* Museenii fi Aaron luboota isaa keessa turan; Saamu'elis immoo warra maqaa isaa waammatan keessaa tokko ture; isaan Waaqayyoon waammatan, innis isaaniif deebise.
\m \bd 7\bd* Inni utubaa duumessaa keessaa isaanitti dubbate, isaan immoo abboommii isaaf dhugaa ba'u, seerrata inni isaaniif kennes eeganiiru.
\m \bd 8\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo gooftaa keenyaa, ati deebii isaaniif kennite; Waaqayyo isa isaaniif dhiisu, hojii isaanii irrattis isa haala isaanitti ba'u taateettaaf. 
\m \bd 9\bd* Waaqayyoon gooftaa keenya ulfinaan ol kaasaa, Waaqayyo gooftaan keenya qulqulluu dha; tulluu isaa isa qulqullaa'aa irratti isaaf sagadaa!
\b 
